room_title: Escape room "The Unreal Room" by Tic Toc Escapes in Raleigh - Durham
room_description: Designed for kids 9 to 13 years old to play on their own without parents.  A game host will be in the room to provide hints to keep the game on track for a fun escape. The goal is to escape the room.  Great for birthday parties!  There is a Party Room available for rent to continue the celebration with pizza and cake.
